summary: An organised, driven, hardworking 3rd year medical student studying Geneeskunde at the Rijksuniversiteit Groningen and participating in the Junior Scientific Masterclass (JSM). A former International Baccalaureate (IB) student with a passion for providing care. A highly positive, approachable individual with good social skills, as well as the ability to take on leadership roles and make critical decisions.
